    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1903-08-29T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1903-08-29T00:00:00-05:00" n="176"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d176">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Beaupré</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">United States Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-08-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 29, 1903</hi>
                        </date>. (Received September 4.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>August 29, 12 m. I have not yet received any messages from the Department
                    concerning the rejection of the treaty nor those mentioned in my telegram of the
                    26th. The committee has not yet reported, and the prospects of satisfactory
                    report are not good.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Beaupré.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
